<P>
* AT&amp;E Corp., San Francisco, has named Thomas L. Leming president of 
Receptor Network Services, a newly created AT&amp;E division, and senior vice 
president of AT&amp;E. Leming previously was a senior vice president at MCI 
Communications. AT&amp;E is developing a wireless communications network. 
