</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
AIRPLANE ACCIDENTS -- COLORADO 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA010689-0086 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 2072 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 6, 1989, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part 1; Page 5; Column 1; Foreign Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
