PROGRAMMING 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA010689-0119 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 2153 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 6, 1989, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
